# Rising Temperature

## Problem Type
Self JOIN

## What I Learned

- Joined the Weather table with itself.
- Compared today's temperature with yesterday's.
- Used date difference while joining.

## Pattern

Need to compare rows from the same table.

Use:
SELF JOIN

## Difficulty

Easy

##Solution

select t.id from Weather w  join Weather t on datediff(t.recordDate,w.recordDate)=1 where t.temperature>w.temperature;
